==English==
===Etymology===
From {{Sp.}} ''[[chaparro]]'', ultimately from [[Basque]] [[tsapar]]
===Noun===
'''chaparral'''

#A region of [[shrub]]s, typically [[dry]] in the [[summer]] and [[rainy]] in the [[winter]]. The coast of the [[Mediterranean]] is such a region.

